  "title": "Senior/Sales Associate (Luxury Ready-To-Wear/Central)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Client &amp; Branding</strong></li>\n  <li>Act as brand ambassador, deliver excellent client experience.</li>\n  <li>Represent brand image and promote collections with strong product knowledge &amp; storytelling.</li>\n  <li><strong>CRM</strong></li>\n  <li>Build and maintain long-term client relationships.</li>\n  <li><strong>Sales</strong></li>\n  <li>Drive to achieve sales targets and KPIs.</li>\n  <li><strong>Operations</strong></li>\n  <li>Adhere to operational processes (cash register, stock, visual merchandising).</li>\n  <li> Carry out other assigned duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min. 1 year experience in fashion retail (ready-to-wear preferred).</li>\n  <li>Client-focused and passionate about fashion.</li>\n  <li>Energetic, positive, and approachable.</li>\n  <li>Sales-driven, target-oriented, able to work under pressure.</li>\n  <li>Basic MS Office skills.</li>\n  <li>More experienced candidates may be considered for Senior Sales Associate.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p>\n<p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p>\n<p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p>\n<p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
